Keyboard Shortcuts for Building Data Prep Recipes

Global Shortcuts:
Ctrl+F (Windows), Cmd+F (macOS) - Move to search bar
Ctrl+/ (Windows), Cmd+/ (macOS) - Open or close Data Prep Keyboard Shortcuts
Ctrl+O (Windows), Cmd+O (macOS) - Add input data
Ctrl+Z (Windows), Cmd+Z (macOS) - Undo last action
Ctrl+Y (Windows), Cmd+Y (macOS) - Redo last undone action
Ctrl+D (Windows), Cmd+D (macOS) - Toggle Data Preview on or off
Ctrl+V (Windows), Cmd+V (macOS) - Open or close Version History panel
Ctrl+S (Windows), Cmd+S (macOS) - Save

Recipe Graph Keyboard Shortcuts:
Arrow key → - Move to next outgoing node
Arrow key ← - Move to closest incoming node
Arrow key ↓ - Move to nearest node below
Arrow key ↑ - Move to nearest node above
Shift+B - Open node's Add Branch menu
Tab - Move to next group of connected nodes
Shift+C - Move to next outgoing link
title: Keyboard Shortcuts for Building Data Prep Recipes in CRM Analytics
